OL,3,CFamilies' lives 'will never be the
OL,4,Csame again' after loved ones killed on
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FOne of Northern Ireland's most senior
OL,8,Fcoroner's has told UTV that families
OL,9,Fhe has met at inquests looking into
OL,10,Ftheir loved one's death on the roads,
OL,11,F'will never be the same again'.
OL,13,FJoe McCrisken spoke exclusively to UTV
OL,14,Fto help raise awareness about the
OL,15,Fdangers of driving under the influence
OL,16,Fof alcohol or drugs during the
OL,17,FChristmas period.
