OL,7,FEarlier this month, he held an inquest
OL,8,Finto the death of a Co Down father,
OL,9,Fkilled in a one vehicle crash in
OL,10,FDecember 2024.
OL,12,F34-year-old John Hanna from
OL,13,FDownpatrick was killed near
OL,14,FBallynahinch on Christmas Eve.
OL,16,FThe father-of-one was using a mobile
OL,17,Fphone and under the influence of
OL,18,Falcohol and cocaine when he crashed
OL,19,Finto a fence on the Downpatrick Road
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
