OL,3,CFamilies' lives 'will never be the
OL,4,Csame again' after loved ones killed on
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FAn inquest found that Mr Hanna was not
OL,8,Fwearing a seatbelt, using his mobile
OL,9,Fphone and speed played a part in the
OL,10,Fcollision.
OL,12,FAll these factors are included in the
OL,13,FPSNI's 'Fatal Five' reasons why people
OL,14,Fare dying on the roads.
OL,16,FPolice tell people to slow down, don't
OL,17,Fbe careless, always wear a seatbelt,
OL,18,Fstay off your mobile phone and never
OL,19,Fdrink or take drugs before driving.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
