OL,3,CFamilies' lives 'will never be the
OL,4,Csame again' after loved ones killed on
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FSenior coroner, Joe McCrisken told UTV
OL,8,FMr Hanna's family had been left
OL,9,Fdevastated by his death.
OL,11,F"When John's father came along to the
OL,12,Finquest and stood up in court to talk
OL,13,Fabout his son, he said he couldn't
OL,14,Ffeel any pride for his son because of
OL,15,Fwhat had happened.
OL,17,F"He was brave coming to the inquest
OL,18,Fand speaking as well as he did, but
OL,19,Fyou could tell that the heart had been
OL,20,Fripped out of that family."
