OL,3,CFamilies' lives 'will never be the
OL,4,Csame again' after loved ones killed on
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FDuring the week leading up to
OL,8,FChristmas 2024 between 20 and
OL,9,FDecemeber 27 - there were eight deaths
OL,10,Fon the roads in NI.
OL,12,FThat is almost as many as any other
OL,13,Fmonth of the whole year.
OL,15,FTo date, more than 2,700 people have
OL,16,Fbeen arrested for driving under the
OL,17,Finfluence of drink or drugs.
OL,19,F52 people have lost their life on the
OL,20,Froads so far in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
